\[
\dot{W}(m,t)=\mu W(m-1,t)-\mu W(m,t)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Solution to the above equation with initial value 
\begin_inset Formula $W(m,0)=\delta_{m,0}$
\end_inset

 is the Poisson distribution 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W(m,t)=\frac{\tau^{m}}{m!}e^{-\tau},\quad\text{with}\,\tau=\mu t
\]

