\begin_layout Itemize
We want to transform old variables 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{x}$
\end_inset

 in new variables 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{x}'$
\end_inset

 with 
\begin_inset Formula $x'_{i}=f_{i}(\boldsymbol{x},t)$
\end_inset

 and express the Fokker-Planck equation in terms of the new variables 
