\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Integrating both sides yields 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\ln W(x)=\int dx\frac{1}{D_{2}(x)}\left[D_{1}(x)-\frac{\partial D_{2}(x)}{\partial x}\right]+N_{0}
\]

\end_inset

which yields 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W(x)=\frac{N_{0}}{D_{2}(x)}e^{\int dx\frac{D_{1}(x)}{D_{2}(x)}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

