Solving the first equation yields 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\phi=ce^{-\lambda t}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Hence, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
W(x,t)=\varphi(x)e^{-\lambda t}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi(x)$
\end_inset

