\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Finite jumps
\series default
: We assume that a finite jump of the potential 
\begin_inset Formula $\Phi(x)=\ln D_{2}(x)-\int dx\frac{D_{1}(x)}{D_{2}(x)}$
\end_inset

 occurs at 
\begin_inset Formula $x=0$
\end_inset


\end_layout

